{"id": "1232284593353392149", "channel_id": "1230861300926779404", "type": 0, "author_id": "1221463356138061828", "author_name": "lilisi123456", "author_bot": false, "content": "报偿打击一阶段也可以收尾，莉莉道中表现会更强", "timestamp": "2024-04-23T10:59:01.796000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1230861300926779404", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "阿格里帕（蜘蛛）食用指南", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1232284980819001364", "channel_id": "1230861300926779404", "type": 0, "author_id": "1215520307519954984", "author_name": "qiyuan48", "author_bot": false, "content": "我不喜歡帶莉莉主要因為莉莉不開狂氣", "timestamp": "2024-04-23T11:00:34.175000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1230861300926779404", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "阿格里帕（蜘蛛）食用指南", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1232285074054053978", "channel_id": "1230861300926779404", "type": 0, "author_id": "1215520307519954984", "author_name": "qiyuan48", "author_bot": false, "content": "但我發現帶環娜好像也沒怎麼開狂🫠", "timestamp": "2024-04-23T11:00:56.404000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1230861300926779404", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "阿格里帕（蜘蛛）食用指南", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1232285347337994280", "channel_id": "1230861300926779404", "type": 0, "author_id": "1221463356138061828", "author_name": "lilisi123456", "author_bot": false, "content": "可以给莉莉带苍白后裔，而且如果只是触发毒的话，莉莉开大限制其实还好，需要抗伤或者面对多段伤害的时候就可以开", "timestamp": "2024-04-23T11:02:01.560000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1230861300926779404", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "阿格里帕（蜘蛛）食用指南", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1232285564666122260", "channel_id": "1230861300926779404", "type": 0, "author_id": "1221463356138061828", "author_name": "lilisi123456", "author_bot": false, "content": "觉醒莉莉的话，还可以多一些鸡毛蒜皮的毒（）👀", "timestamp": "2024-04-23T11:02:53.375000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1230861300926779404", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "阿格里帕（蜘蛛）食用指南", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1232290089175093350", "channel_id": "1230861300926779404", "type": 0, "author_id": "960513153240825907", "author_name": "dyyqcwj", "author_bot": false, "content": "看到跟我不一样的阵容我去试了一下（我上期攻略活动发了蜘蛛攻略），超出两回合（正好在你下面），开始不清楚要用命定补伤害把他卖了，现在可以确定的是娜娜的作用特别小，开狂气爆发的次数太少了，作用是2费卡找回旋，相应的这个操作能用环娜的钥令解决，最重要的是打精英怪太慢，亏血严重，如果是莉莉会打得更快，说苍白后裔和大招的事的话，莉莉主要是在靠报偿打击触发毒和斩难缠的怪上起作用，镜像报偿打击和携带锁链能让回合结束的更快，且莉莉在队伍里血量上限更高，在高难环境里肯定是莉莉最优（我已经拿蜘蛛打了两期5-3了），不否认环娜是比较好的替代，但是仍然是莉莉下位，莉莉挂机还能享受0费出牌，娜娜有点难说了就", "timestamp": "2024-04-23T11:20:52.102000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1230861300926779404", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "阿格里帕（蜘蛛）食用指南", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1232290335011504208", "channel_id": "1230861300926779404", "type": 0, "author_id": "960513153240825907", "author_name": "dyyqcwj", "author_bot": false, "content": "已经是接近完美（除了石碑给我变了脐带）的造物了，依然超了两回合，娜娜十回合全程挂机。。。", "timestamp": "2024-04-23T11:21:50.714000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1232290334789074944", "filename": "Screenshot_20240423_181025_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 187251, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1230861300926779404/1232290334789074944/Screenshot_20240423_181025_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbae4e&is=69ca5cce&hm=f3249db2658c8ef780c36c08c4d9fea31e0afb5f3475b98da1b01f0888e30ea7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1230861300926779404", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "阿格里帕（蜘蛛）食用指南", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1232290557011824801", "channel_id": "1230861300926779404", "type": 0, "author_id": "960513153240825907", "author_name": "dyyqcwj", "author_bot": false, "content": "挂机问题相当严重，而且哪怕是在这么强力的时灵摆下打精英怪都很折磨，最佳还是莉莉罢", "timestamp": "2024-04-23T11:22:43.643000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1230861300926779404", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "阿格里帕（蜘蛛）食用指南", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1232291313655873536", "channel_id": "1230861300926779404", "type": 0, "author_id": "960513153240825907", "author_name": "dyyqcwj", "author_bot": false, "content": "在打高难时，诺缔拉补防御端也是很优的，毕竟活的久了伤害也会高，这期5-3对蜘蛛来说前期压力较大，我带了三生存", "timestamp": "2024-04-23T11:25:44.041000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1230861300926779404", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "阿格里帕（蜘蛛）食用指南", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179734373019748"]}
