{"id": "1232291707119210556", "channel_id": "1230861300926779404", "type": 0, "author_id": "960513153240825907", "author_name": "dyyqcwj", "author_bot": false, "content": "关于SSR命轮，陨日有暴击率保底，确实不错，但是考虑到密契和造物对暴击有补正，血肉狂宴的上限会更高，密契有做暴击率的话，可以尝试一下，3叠一吞也有额外的10力量，不少了😘", "timestamp": "2024-04-23T11:27:17.850000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1230861300926779404", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "阿格里帕（蜘蛛）食用指南", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179734373019748"]}
